{
  "stem": "1338.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came back, I tried to go back to Auschwitz to the plant to find Leib, but [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think you are going to the-- the end of the fourth tape.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what happened next?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, next I worked in some other place, taken to whatever places they took you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I felt pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, my mother was not to be found.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't show up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, she didn't know what happened to me when I disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, when I came back, it was too late to make contact with her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, the selections would come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every Sunday afternoon, there was a selection, Jews only.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very tough to survive, continuously.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I became very adept at surviving despite that Leib thought that I will never be able to survive because I am too naive and don't know the rules of this game of the cruel world.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In my own, amicable way, I managed to avoid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had one instant, which I-- probably left me with a big scar in my-- I never-- I come-- my father was a very proud man, as you probably understand from  the-- probably to the point of a little bit annoyance and maybe a little bit exaggeration.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I probably inherited that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was proud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't begging for anything, ever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I begged for my life once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a Polish man, head of the barrack, who always sat there and listened to my screaming to my mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a beautiful Polish accent, always did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was somehow impressed by that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in one of the selections, somebody else was marking me for-- and I turned to him, and he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
